    Class Real

    This class stores a Real Number as a double.

    It is implemented to be used with RealVector.java

    For further information, contact with the author via e-mail: alu0100881622@ull.edu.es

      • major

        public Real major(Real numeroReal)
        This method returns the biggest number of two given Real numbers.

        Its implementation takes into account the fact that the method is finished since a return sentence is executed. Because of that, else sentence is not needed.
        Parameters:
        numeroReal - One of two Real numbers to compare
        Returns:
        The biggest of the two numbers
